  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 47a621783cb453147b01764dde5ed130, type: 3}
  m_Name: RosellaIntro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPCDialogue
  dialogueLines:
  - Oh! A human actually walked in this time.
  - Well... half-human-world, anyway.
  - My name is Rosella. I sell magical seeds here. Infused black roses, stars...
    the usual.
  - Or, well, what's left... of the usual.
  - Magic's gotten weaker over the years. Harder for crops to grow properly now.
  - Harder for fairies to fly, too...
  - Still! No point sulking about it all day.
  - If you're really Selene's apprentice, you'll probably need seeds sooner or later.
  - Just try not to kill them immediately with your pickaxe, alright?
